{"tid":748003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係話我唔想孝順","createTime":"2018-07-19T01:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T02:24:21.000Z","uid":135784,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"20c668728418c6a388a680489564230e9c5e00fc","tid":748003,"uid":135784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:10:28.000Z","msg":"不過同啲老一輩出街真係好撚辛苦<br />\n<br />\n完全想扮唔識佢地<br />\n<br />\n係地鐵到企就攬住條柱 講電話大聲到成卡都聽到 <br />\n<br />\n之後大大聲問我係咪下個站落車<br />\n<br />\n果下我想死呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n好啦 之後去餐廳食野 冇啦啦拎部電話出嚟聽粵曲<br />\n<br />\n冇錯！又係大大聲 成個餐廳啲人望曬過嚟 我即刻扮搭枱<br />\n<br />\n就算出聲提下佢 轉個頭又會係咁<br />\n<br />\n老一輩啲人其實係咪唔識尊重人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c9ee652da060c1f83a4b82436b6b55cbc5a616","tid":748003,"uid":135784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:11:25.000Z","msg":"要個細既嚟提你 我自己都唔好意思啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb997c7464675c3a788146470d31a8222ead46d2","tid":748003,"uid":135784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:12:48.000Z","msg":"完全唔會考慮下其他人既感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47b5101c866ecc45cfc5aeaeb2b8549cd6b0076","tid":748003,"uid":161195,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:13:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46e6823e3587fb4ca04c1bbad7204e63dd52f9e5","tid":748003,"uid":135784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:14:21.000Z","msg":"係咪以前社會環境係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9078d776f8db824dfe0e43958f9c5d38db7fdb","tid":748003,"uid":12994,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f9c9ee652da060c1f83a4b82436b6b55cbc5a616","tid":748003,"uid":135784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:11:25.000Z","msg":"要個細既嚟提你 我自己都唔好意思啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor